{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":990,"text":"Hi. This is my mobile phone."},{"time":8535,"text":"A mobile phone can change your life,"},{"time":15978,"text":"and a mobile phone gives you individual freedom."},{"time":24810,"text":"With a mobile phone,"},{"time":27178,"text":"you can shoot a crime against humanity in Syria."},{"time":31962,"text":"With a mobile phone,"},{"time":33914,"text":"you can tweet a message"},{"time":36202,"text":"and start a protest in Egypt."},{"time":42045,"text":"And with a mobile phone,"},{"time":44522,"text":"you can record a song, load it up to"},{"time":47443,"text":"SoundCloud and become famous."},{"time":49924,"text":"All this is possible with your mobile phone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":54494,"text":"I'm a child of 1984,"},{"time":56543,"text":"and I live in the city of Berlin."},{"time":59904,"text":"Let's go back to that time, to this city."},{"time":65584,"text":"Here you can see"},{"time":66823,"text":"how hundreds of thousands of people"},{"time":69007,"text":"stood up and protested for change."},{"time":73246,"text":"This is autumn 1989,"},{"time":76432,"text":"and imagine that all those people standing up"},{"time":81055,"text":"and protesting for change had a"},{"time":83864,"text":"mobile phone in their pocket."}]},{"cues":[{"time":87024,"text":"Who in the room has a mobile phone with you?"},{"time":88751,"text":"Hold it up."},{"time":89886,"text":"Hold your phones up, hold your phones up!"},{"time":93015,"text":"Hold it up. An Android, a Blackberry, wow."},{"time":95741,"text":"That's a lot. Almost everybody today has a mobile phone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102134,"text":"But today I will talk about me and my mobile phone,"},{"time":106686,"text":"and how it changed my life."},{"time":110203,"text":"And I will talk about this."},{"time":113783,"text":"These are 35,830 lines of information."},{"time":118886,"text":"Raw data."},{"time":121649,"text":"And why are these informations there?"},{"time":126275,"text":"Because in the summer of 2006,"},{"time":129256,"text":"the E.U. Commission tabled a directive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":132743,"text":"This directive [is] called Data Retention Directive."},{"time":137408,"text":"This directive says that each phone company in Europe,"},{"time":141767,"text":"each Internet service company all over Europe,"},{"time":146264,"text":"has to store a wide range of information about the users."},{"time":151543,"text":"Who calls whom? Who sends whom an email?"},{"time":154704,"text":"Who sends whom a text message?"},{"time":156848,"text":"And if you use your mobile phone, where you are."},{"time":161183,"text":"All this information is stored for at least six months,"},{"time":165635,"text":"up to two years by your phone company"},{"time":168919,"text":"or your Internet service provider."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174991,"text":"And all over Europe, people stood up and said,"},{"time":178651,"text":"\"We don't want this.\""},{"time":181158,"text":"They said, we don't want this data retention."},{"time":184556,"text":"We want self-determination in the digital age,"},{"time":188093,"text":"and we don't want that phone companies and Internet companies"},{"time":191092,"text":"have to store all this information about us."},{"time":194541,"text":"They were lawyers, journalists, priests,"},{"time":197224,"text":"they all said: \"We don't want this.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":200380,"text":"And here you can see, like 10 thousands of people"},{"time":203447,"text":"went out on the streets of Berlin and said,"},{"time":206103,"text":"\"Freedom, not fear.\""},{"time":209310,"text":"And some even said, this would be Stasi 2.0."},{"time":213759,"text":"Stasi was the secret police in East Germany."}]},{"cues":[{"time":219796,"text":"And I also ask myself, does it really work?"},{"time":224277,"text":"Can they really store all this information about us?"},{"time":227709,"text":"Every time I use my mobile phone?"},{"time":231354,"text":"So I asked my phone company, Deutsche Telekom,"},{"time":235110,"text":"which was at that time the largest phone company in Germany,"},{"time":238875,"text":"and I asked them, please,"},{"time":240271,"text":"send me all the information you have stored about me."},{"time":244642,"text":"And I asked them once, and I asked them again,"},{"time":246801,"text":"and I got no real answer. It was only blah blah answers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249977,"text":"But then I said, I want to have this information,"},{"time":253089,"text":"because this is my life you are protocoling."},{"time":257841,"text":"So I decided to start a lawsuit against them,"},{"time":261833,"text":"because I wanted to have this information."},{"time":264793,"text":"But Deutsche Telekom said, no,"},{"time":266793,"text":"we will not give you this information."},{"time":269545,"text":"So at the end, I had a settlement with them."},{"time":273762,"text":"I'll put down the lawsuit"},{"time":275121,"text":"and they will send me all the information I ask for."},{"time":278329,"text":"Because in the mean time,"},{"time":279546,"text":"the German Constitutional Court ruled"},{"time":281783,"text":"that the implementation of this E.U. directive"},{"time":285600,"text":"into German law was unconstitutional."}]},{"cues":[{"time":290019,"text":"So I got this ugly brown envelope"},{"time":292137,"text":"with a C.D. inside."},{"time":294705,"text":"And on the C.D., this was on."},{"time":297785,"text":"Thirty-five thousand eight hundred thirty lines of information."},{"time":303146,"text":"At first I saw it, and I said, okay,"},{"time":305561,"text":"it's a huge file. Okay."},{"time":308964,"text":"But then after a while I realized,"},{"time":311481,"text":"this is my life."},{"time":313769,"text":"This is six months of my life,"},{"time":315553,"text":"into this file."}]},{"cues":[{"time":319851,"text":"So I was a little bit skeptical, what should I do with it?"},{"time":324101,"text":"Because you can see where I am,"},{"time":327280,"text":"where I sleep at night,"},{"time":329488,"text":"what I am doing."},{"time":334192,"text":"But then I said, I want to go out with this information."},{"time":338785,"text":"I want to make them public."},{"time":340561,"text":"Because I want to show the people what does data retention mean."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344975,"text":"So together with Zeit Online and Open Data City, I did this."},{"time":350239,"text":"This is a visualization of six months of my life."},{"time":354367,"text":"You can zoom in and zoom out,"},{"time":356255,"text":"you can wind back and fast forward."},{"time":358704,"text":"You can see every step I take."},{"time":362122,"text":"And you can even see"},{"time":364447,"text":"how I go from Frankfurt by train"},{"time":367496,"text":"to Cologne, and how often I call in between."}]},{"cues":[{"time":371728,"text":"All this is possible with this information."},{"time":376461,"text":"That's a little bit scary."},{"time":381916,"text":"But it is not only about me."},{"time":387416,"text":"It's about all of us."},{"time":389816,"text":"First, it's only like, I call my wife and she calls me,"},{"time":394540,"text":"and we talk to each other a couple of times."},{"time":397211,"text":"And then there are some friends calling me,"},{"time":399673,"text":"and they call each other."},{"time":401601,"text":"And after a while you are calling you,"},{"time":403720,"text":"and you are calling you, and you have this great"},{"time":405984,"text":"communication network."}]},{"cues":[{"time":408408,"text":"But you can see how your people are communicating with each other,"},{"time":412889,"text":"what times they call each other, when they go to bed."},{"time":416192,"text":"You can see all of this."},{"time":418346,"text":"You can see the hubs, like who are the leaders in the group."},{"time":422361,"text":"If you have access to this information,"},{"time":425841,"text":"you can see what your society is doing."},{"time":429688,"text":"If you have access to this information,"},{"time":432313,"text":"you can control your society."}]},{"cues":[{"time":436730,"text":"This is a blueprint for countries like China and Iran."},{"time":441706,"text":"This is a blueprint how to survey your society,"},{"time":445874,"text":"because you know who talks to whom,"},{"time":448490,"text":"who sends whom an email, all this is possible"},{"time":451371,"text":"if you have access to this information."},{"time":454069,"text":"And this information is stored for at least six months"},{"time":457106,"text":"in Europe, up to two years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":462093,"text":"Like I said at the beginning,"},{"time":463708,"text":"imagine that all those people on the streets of Berlin"},{"time":467141,"text":"in autumn of 1989"},{"time":469589,"text":"had a mobile phone in their pocket."},{"time":472612,"text":"And the Stasi would have known who took part at this protest,"},{"time":476581,"text":"and if the Stasi would have known"},{"time":478268,"text":"who are the leaders behind it,"},{"time":481762,"text":"this may never have happened."},{"time":484983,"text":"The fall of the Berlin Wall would maybe not [have been] there."},{"time":488014,"text":"And in the aftermath, also not the fall of the Iron Curtain."},{"time":491630,"text":"Because today, state agencies and companies"},{"time":496238,"text":"want to store as much information as they can get about us,"},{"time":500527,"text":"online and offline."},{"time":502407,"text":"They want to have the possibility to track our lives,"},{"time":506614,"text":"and they want to store them for all time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":510462,"text":"But self-determination and living in the digital age"},{"time":514905,"text":"is no contradiction."},{"time":517602,"text":"But you have to fight for your self-determination today."},{"time":522761,"text":"You have to fight for it every day."},{"time":526788,"text":"So, when you go home,"},{"time":529550,"text":"tell your friends"},{"time":531206,"text":"that privacy is a value of the 21st century,"},{"time":535517,"text":"and it's not outdated."},{"time":538037,"text":"When you go home, tell your representative"},{"time":542103,"text":"only because companies and state agencies have the possibility"},{"time":546582,"text":"to store certain information, they don't have to do it."},{"time":551998,"text":"And if you don't believe me,"},{"time":554343,"text":"ask your phone company what information they store about you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":561966,"text":"So, in the future, every time you use your mobile phone,"},{"time":568826,"text":"let it be a reminder to you"},{"time":571898,"text":"that you have to fight for self-determination in the digital age."},{"time":575665,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":576890,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}